      "label": "Post-Gospel Stichera",
      "note": "On Sundays: one of the 11 stichera matching the Gospel number, preceded by 'Glory… Through the prayers of the Apostles…' and 'Now… Through the prayers of the Theotokos…'. On feasts: appointed stichera.",
